@0 = ~Ah... I'd heard rumors that our esteemed hero was to return to us. Welcome back, <CHARNAME>. After your long journey, I trust your stay will be a restful one.~
@1 = ~Adventurers, welcome to the Three Old Kegs. I trust your stay will be a restful one.~
@2 = ~And how has the city fared in my absence?~
@3 = ~Between the chaos in the aftermath of your trial, Skie Silvershield's death, and the refugee crisis, it's a wonder that the city didn't tear itself apart. Fortunately the situation has improved of late, especially with Skie restored and the refugees resettled.~
@4 = ~Thank you, Ithtyl. It's good to be back.~
@5 = ~I was hoping for a little more excitement. It seems this place is as dull as ever.~
@6 = ~I might suggest the Blushing Mermaid as one alternative. They are somewhat lax in the area of house rules. Good day.~
@7 = ~Indeed. Now, if you'll excuse me, I have many financial matters that require my attention.~
@8 = ~Welcome to the Three Old Kegs. I trust your stay will be a restful one.~